title: Removed icon and label from manifest
message:
Removed icon and label from manifest

Removed icon and label from the AndroidManifest.xml of the library since a) it's not needed and b) if the library is added with gradle, it will produce this error, which can be fixed easily but it's easier to just remove it from the library: [...] Attribute icon from AndroidManifest.xml is also present at com.pnikosis:materialish-progress:1.0:14:9 [...] Suggestion: add 'tools:replace="android:label"' to <application> element at AndroidManifest.xml to override
